{"tid":1268952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港電台發聲明嚴厲譴責在場人士阻撓及辱罵本台記者","createTime":"2019-06-30T12:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T12:23:00.000Z","uid":240362,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2c31aeb28c905d50fcf9b8eee8795a4779aac5cb","tid":1268952,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:08:38.000Z","msg":"金鐘添馬公園舉行「撐警大會」，本台多名記者在採訪期間，受到集會人士不斷滋擾，包括全程用手機拍攝、用以粗口謾罵；其中一名女記者被一名集會男子捉著手，最終要由警員及其他記者護送離開。香港電台發表聲明，嚴厲譴責在場人士多番阻撓及以粗言穢語辱罵本台記者。<br />\n<br />\n2019-06-30 19:59:24<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1465849-20190630.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1465849-20190630.htm&d=ZcVshzlQZ77dxUPC5JM1BEkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=1c14b0fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1465849-20190630.htm&h=a11d432b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1465849-20190630.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4c0e4e4f1b4cc8f7ccd825f21ab8e75904e80619","tid":1268952,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:15:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8pAyEOY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8pAyEOY.jpg&h=6abdede8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[ 備戰 ] 夢境作戰訓話 + 整合Post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1267323/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1267323/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人到而家仲未識真正咁運用三角鐵馬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1267307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1267307</a>"},{"pid":"fc360e27603e8bc796f872968872cf87c61b8003","tid":1268952,"uid":221265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:21:08.000Z","msg":"Cctvb今次冇發聲明<br />\n<br />\n應該俾撐警廢老攬住錫緊"},{"pid":"d99ff5983defc1f2ca5027669c2bfebb06d3c2ae","tid":1268952,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"